author: brane
msg: * libsvn_subr/config.c (read_all): Keep the same arg list on all platforms.
On Win32, let the caller decide whether or not to read the registry.
Fixed the docstring, and added a note about how the order might be wrong.
(svn_config_read_proxies): Introduced new vars for registry paths, so
that read_all can be wrapped in SVN_ERR.

msg: * COMMITTERS: Add self with commit access to doc.

author: brane
msg: Scratch another Win32 itch: Support drive letters in file:// URLs.
